text: "Stupid Cupid" is a 1958 song written by Neil Sedaka and became a hit for Connie Francis. It went to number 14 in the United States and Sedaka himself released his version in 1959. ==References== Category:1958 songs Category:Neil Sedaka songs Category:Connie Francis songs Category:Patsy Cline songs Category:Mandy Moore songs Category:Wanda Jackson songs
